latestIgtvVideos.title: GOA VLOG 2021🌴
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Put your hands in mine. You know that I want to be with you all the time💖 @aditiivyas @dakshabhamblani23 @aayushi_barot @naiya_kothari @namu_8135 
Okay so this was my first trip with my friends and I directly took permission for GOA from my parents because I wanted my first trip to be the most memorable. And guess what, no matter wherever I’ll go on other places with them, this trip to goa will be always special because we made some hilarious memories there💖 
It was really difficult to convince my dad because tbh I’m a child with weak immune system so he is very protective but I convinced him and I made it! 
Thanks for watching this vlog and reading this story. Love you guys xx
